msgstr ""
"Seleziona **🖨 > i-doit > Cambia Oggetti**, quindi filtra per categoria e/o "
"nome."

#: ../extras/i-doit-track-company-property.rst:51
msgid ""
"Once assets have been linked to a ticket, they can be accessed directly from "
