msgid "(Screencast) See a list of all tickets for an asset in i-doit"
msgstr "(Screencast) Vedere un elenco di tutti i ticket per un asset in i-doit"

#: ../extras/i-doit-track-company-property.rst:69
msgid ""
"Click the 💬 in the toolbar to list an asset's tickets. Use the **🔗 Open in "
